OL,3,GStrathclyde
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FAny overnight fog and low cloud
OL,6,Fdispersing this morning. Otherwise it
OL,7,Fwill be dry with plenty of sunshine.
OL,8,FWarm, locally very warm across western
OL,9,FArgyll.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FThis evening will be dry with
OL,12,Fsome late sunshine. Then the rest of
OL,13,Fthe night will be dry and clear with
OL,14,Fsome patchy fog and low cloud.
OL,15,
OL,16,CFriday:FDry with some sunshine in the
OL,17,Fmorning. Clouding over from the
OL,18,Fsouthwest in the afternoon with some
OL,19,Fshowery rain extending northeast. Warm.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
